			"a_h2": "Built From This",
			"a_description": "The distinctive visual aesthetic of Neumorphism — a design approach that creates unique, memorable interfaces. Background: light (#e0e5ec). The .inner panel has a clean background with subtle border treatment and appropriate border-radius. Colors: #6366f1 as the primary accent for interactive elements and highlights. #2a2a3a for headings, #6a6a7a for body text. The aesthetic captures the essence of neumorphism through careful color choices, spacing, and visual weight. Set in Rubik — chosen for its visual character that complements this design style. Heading at weight 600-700, 24-28px, line-height 1.2-1.3. Eyebrow at weight 500, 11px, uppercase, 2-3px letter-spacing, color #6366f1. Body at weight 400, 14-15px, line-height 1.6-1.7, color #6a6a7a. Buttons: primary — #6366f1 background with contrasting text. Secondary: transparent with #6366f1 border. Alternatives: system-ui (universal fallback), sans-serif stack.",
